name: Coleman Prairie Breeze 9 Person Cabin Tent
shortDescription: The Coleman Prairie Breeze 9 Person Cabin Tent features 6 oversize windows and a built-in fan and LED lighting system.
longDescription: The Coleman Prairie Breeze 9 Person Cabin Tent boasts 140 sq. ft. of living space that can fit 2 queen-size airbeds and sleep up to 9 people. The 6 oversize windows provide plenty of ventilation, while the built-in 2-speed fan can cast a cool breeze or exhaust hot air with a push of the illuminated wall switch.

name: Magellan Outdoors Men's Aransas Pass Short Sleeve Gingham Fishing Shirt
shortDescription: The Magellan Outdoors™ Men's Aransas Pass Short Sleeve Gingham Fishing Shirt is made of polyester and features MagWick fabric technology.
longDescription: The Magellan Outdoors™ Men's Aransas Pass Short Sleeve Gingham Fishing Shirt is made of 100% polyester with a mesh lining for breathable, comfortable wear and features sweat-wicking MagWick fabric technology to help keep you cool. MagShield technology offers UPF 30 sun protection to help you stay safe outdoors. 2 chest pockets. Button-down closure. Checkered pattern.

name: Magellan Outdoors Men's Grand Pass Jacket
longDescription: Stay warm during the cold days of whitetail season with the Magellan Outdoors Men's Grand Pass CVC Duck Jacket.  Front kangaroo pockets with reinforced rivets at the corners easily accomodate gloved hands and will hold up to repeated use.  An attached hood with adjustable drawstring stands at the ready for when the weather takes a turn for the worse, while the knit cuffs and hem help hold in your body heat and keep the wind and elements out.  The 100% polyester lining allows easy on and off without bunching your layers and the Realtree camo outer keeps you concealed from your prey.
imageAltDescription: Magellan Outdoors Men's Grand Pass Jacket

name: Magellan Outdoors Men's Hunt Gear Knit Camo Shirt
shortDescription: The Magellan Outdoors Men's Hunt Gear Knit Camo Shirt is designed with long sleeves and a crew-neck collar.
longDescription: Your collection of hunting gear isn't complete until you add the Magellan Outdoors Men's Hunt Gear Knit Camo Shirt. With moisture-wicking fabric and UPF 15 sun protection, this shirt helps keep you dry and comfortable while out in the wild. Its long-sleeve, classic design offers versatile wear, and the camo pattern delivers the concealment you need.
